patthana16.89:1.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ rūpāvacaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho narūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha …pe… ārammaṇe tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
patthana16.89:2.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ narūpāvacaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho nanarūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā tīṇi …pe… avigate tīṇi.
